        "content_domains, audience_profile, evidence_points, text_findings, numeric_findings, important_columns, "
        "and recommended_actions must each be arrays of concise Chinese strings only.\n"
        "subject_type must be one of: social_account, customer_entity, product_entity, transaction_entity, document_entity, generic_subject.\n"
        "metric_cards must be an array of objects with keys: metric, role, business_meaning, management_impact, caution.\n"
        "Do not use nested JSON objects in any field except metric_cards.\n"
